gdlex-ocr (0.1.9) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix system tray icon initialization to prevent double-registration on KDE.
  * Remove KDE hide-to-tray notification that caused an unwanted "i" icon badge.
  * Theme folder icons in Qt file dialogs to match the system icon theme.
  * Harden OCRmyPDF subprocess: explicit UTF-8 encoding with errors="replace",
    process termination on callback exception, and "--" separator before paths.
  * Guard _cancelled visibility check with isVisible() to avoid late widget
    access after window close.
  * Add offline subprocess stress test covering error-path and encoding edge
    cases.
  * Cover folder-matrix.svg asset in packaging and doctor checks.

