gdlex-ocr (0.1.5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add optional local OCR backends and runtime diagnostics.
  * Add the "PDF già ricercabile" profile for already-searchable PDFs.
  * Improve "Accurato testo" so OCRmyPDF/Tesseract creates a searchable PDF
    that is then used as the Docling source.
  * Avoid using Docling/RapidOCR internal OCR as the primary source for
    Italian scanned PDFs when using "Accurato testo".
  * Extend manifests with OCR backend metadata, Markdown structure metadata,
    and bookmarks.reason.
  * Improve Markdown heading generation and bookmark strategy selection.
  * Reorganize the "PDF e output" GUI section into Base and Backend OCR tabs.
  * Add a GUI screenshot helper with automatic virtualenv re-exec.
  * Document the future Portale/TIAP criminal case bundle milestone.
  * Expand offline tests to 226.

